# ML models — tracked in git (small enough; use Git LFS for large files if needed)
# *.pkl — intentionally NOT ignored so Dockerfile can COPY models/
# Ignore only intermediate/training artifacts:
training/data/*.pkl
scripts/*.pkl

# Large real-world datasets (recreate with scripts/download_real_datasets.py)
# Files exceed GitHub 100 MB limit — use Git LFS or regenerate locally
